---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="excedente"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-surplus"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--wide">
        <div class="wheat-surplus-grid wheat-items-center">
            <div class="wheat-surplus-col-left wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center">
                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-w-full wheat-surplus-visual wheat-p-4 wheat-p-8@md wheat-flex wheat-flex-col-reverse wheat-items-center wheat-gap-1 wheat-overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--9"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--8"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--7"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--6"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--5"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--4"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--3"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--2"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-surplus-grain wheat-surplus-grain--1"></div>

                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-surplus-caption wheat-font-mono">
                        FIG. 4: ACUMULACIÓN
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-surplus-col-right wheat-space-y-8">
                <div>
                    <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-surplus-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase">
                        El Excedente
                    </span>
                    <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-4xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-surplus-title wheat-mt-4">
                        El nacimiento de la pobreza
                    </h2>
                </div>

                <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-surplus-desc">
                    El trigo tiene una property que la carne no tiene: <strong class="wheat-font-bold wheat-surplus-strong">Se puede almacenar</strong>. Un grano seco dura años. Y aquí nace la tragedia humana.
                </p>

                <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-surplus-desc">
                    <ShareableQuote quote="El trigo inventó la pobreza." /> Porque por primera vez, alguien
                    podía tener 'todo' y otro podía no tener 'nada'.
                </p>

                <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-surplus-desc">
                    Si puedes acumular comida, puedes acumular poder. Aparecen los silos. Aparecen
                    los muros para proteger los silos. Aparecen los soldados para vigilar los muros.
                    Aparecen los reyes para contar el grano.
                </p>

                <div class="wheat-surplus-card wheat-p-4 wheat-p-6@md wheat-rounded wheat-border">
                    <h3 class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-font-bold wheat-surplus-card-title wheat-mb-2">La Duda</h3>
                    <p class="wheat-text-sm wheat-text-base@md wheat-surplus-card-desc">
                        Antes del trigo, todos éramos iguales ante el hambre. El grano rompió el
                        equilibrio social para siempre. ¿Construimos las ciudades para protegernos a
                        nosotros, o para proteger al trigo de los demás?
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-surplus {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-surplus-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        width: 100%;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-surplus-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: 3rem;
        }
        .wheat-surplus-col-left {
            grid-column: span 5;
        }
        .wheat-surplus-col-right {
            grid-column: span 7;
        }
        .wheat-p-8\@md {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .wheat-p-6\@md {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
    }
    .wheat-surplus-visual {
        max-width: 20rem;
        aspect-ratio: 1/1;
        background-color: #0c0a09;
        border: 1px solid rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.2);
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-surplus-visual {
            max-width: 100%;
        }
    }
    .wheat-surplus-grain {
        width: 100%;
        height: 0.75rem;
        background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.4);
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-surplus-grain {
            height: 1rem;
        }
    }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--9 { width: 100%; }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--8 { width: 90%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.3); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--7 { width: 80%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.4); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--6 { width: 70%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.5); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--5 { width: 60%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.6); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--4 { width: 50%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.7); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--3 { width: 40%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.8); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--2 { width: 30%; background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.9); }
    .wheat-surplus-grain--1 {
        width: 20%;
        background-color: #92400e;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    }
    .wheat-surplus-caption {
        top: 0.5rem;
        right: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 10px;
        color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-surplus-caption {
            top: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    }
    .wheat-surplus-chapter {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-surplus-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-surplus-desc {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-surplus-strong {
        color: #ffffff;
    }
    .wheat-surplus-card {
        background-color: #292524;
        border-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-surplus-card-title {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-surplus-card-desc {
        color: #78716c;
    }
</style>
